Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:12.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance\Nwith Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that \Nthe prize for a fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,event was the Flare-Flare \NFruit, he decided to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first round is a battle royal\Nwhere only one can win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burgess from the Blackbeard Pirates won\Nthe match of Block A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the battle of Block B has begun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Competitors led by Dagama, the tactician,\Nare protecting Elizabello II,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the king of Prodence Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is he going to throw\Nthe devastating King Punch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Atrocious"! "Evil"!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the words only fitting to this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the top contender\Nto beat Elizabello II after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime,\Nthe Jiaokungdo martial artist - Blue Gilly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the mysterious gladiator - Ricky,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe two strong men are fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4000 Brick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do?!\NHack is the one who collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of monster are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Deadly Blow!\NThe Astonishing King Punch!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hack got defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't even reach Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Bartolomeo do to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I was rooting for Hack!\NThat chicken head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyats-{\i1}san{\i0}, you have to be fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see a clear winner yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B Block - 24 competitors remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be over soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's got a wound or two now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's about time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerful competitors are getting eliminated\None after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following Hack's defeat,\Nthe unknown gladiator,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ricky, also got taken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Gilly is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Blue Gilly-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\N--So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you can cut
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with such a blunt sword, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I can't fight aging.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand all this cheering.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand you, Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't that many men left\Nthanks to Dagama's tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the competitors are gone\Nexcept for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe I'm still here.\NI'm glad that I allied with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Dagama gives us the cue,\Nwe'll disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll fight amongst ourselves\Nuntil one of us wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take down as many \Nenemies as possible for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Gilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Take care of Blue Gilly\Nwhile we're fighting together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a fine job, you stupid dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you haven't given us the cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he... Hey, Dagama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I've been told to hunt you dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you plotting together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get rid of us from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pay you later!\NYour job is done now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warriors who can't use their brains
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just end up as someone's \Npuppets on a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you, Longfeet man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now you turned your back to me,\Nyou're dead, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue Gilly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We of the Prodence Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,will win the Flare-Flare Fruit\Nat any cost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed me, Blue Gilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama the tactician got eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Way to go, Longfeet guy!\N--Blue Gilly-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe people would trust a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dubious guy like him\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? On the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go, Bellamy!\N--Kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our man - Bellamy is beginning to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His target is the "most annoying pirate\Nwho should just go away"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy who went in for the attack\Nis down on the floor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Bartolomeo do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy delivered an attack\Nand got hurt like Hack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...struggling like this right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Death Knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our man - Bellamy is worn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of Devil Fruit did he eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no interest in the Flare-Flare Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have my own reason to win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get on board Doflamingo's \Nship to ride through the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"wild wave" that will come sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done picking on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellamy! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what are you gonna do, Elizabello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is more helpless than a king\Nwithout his court.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody was dying to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people who had been guarding you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhave turned against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything \Nwithout Dagama, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'm all set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do is throw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the ones who were protected
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while we were in that battle formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because nothing is more dangerous \Nthan an exposed blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, you punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report about \Nthe king of Prodence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said he destroyed an
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,enemy country's fort\Nwith a single punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He must've used some kind of weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they say it could take down\Neven the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true, he's gonna throw a punch that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will destroy this part of the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He can't throw such a destructive punch\Nat a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a restlessness in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king who kept quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the battle formation is\Nnow on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the Prodence Kingdom will win\Nthe Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?\NWhat do you wanna talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, in order to \Ndestroy the SMILE factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta beat up someone in the Doflamingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy! I've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I have no time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have nothing to talk about, I'm gonna go now!\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep talking about this radical plan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why do you want to do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you know things\Nthat ordinary people don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your true purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, we better go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, he really did destroy the fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so persistent!\NWhat's this?! Get it off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Don't underestimate \Nthe power of my spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill Elizabello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in the Colosseum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How powerful was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone in the \Nring could survive that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabello II wiped out all of his enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a single punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a hell of a punch!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen something like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy! Blue Gilly!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all other potential \Nwinners have been eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle royal of Block B - 138 \Ncompetitors - the winner is from
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Prodence Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! Somebody's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see? Right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience in that direction \Ndidn't get blown away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbecause of his defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can create barriers\Nby crossing their fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common knowledge!\NEven kids know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a barrier human who ate \Nthe Barrier-Barrier Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fighting King" - Elizabello \NII got knocked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of Block B is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go away!\N--Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That strange guy won.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will dedicate the Flare-Flare Fruit\Nto that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.15,0:22:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're plotting to destroy the factory, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! My friends and I have been\Ncarrying out preparations for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where it is!\NI'll destroy it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we want to save the \Nworkers in the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The workers in the factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.57,0:22:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan could lead to \Nthe fall of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt's a big project!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the nerve and are \Ndetermined to go against Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you everything\Nabout this tragic kingdom - Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
